task.summary: Eliminando angularjs 2, se tendrá un proyecto aparte para el frontend
Created Sessions controller, Entity and Tables
Implementada vista de todos los cortes y detalle de corte
Agregada migracion de creacion de tabla de postes (power_poles)
Added Model and table of supported companies for power poles
Added filter options for autocomplete on power poles, by code
Created relationship between power_poles and scheduled_outages, in order to asign them in outage creation
